nes in the past. In August of 2005, Robertson called for the assassination of Venezuelan President Hugo Ch\u00e1vez, for which he apologized two days later. In January 2006, Robertson said that former Israeli Prime Minister Ariel Sharon's stroke was \"divine retribution\" for pulling Israelis out of the Gaza Strip."}
