nited States who equipped the terrorists. These claims have been denied by Washington.\nThe elections will be held June 12. On Friday, the presidential campaign offices were also attacked by gunmen.\nThursday was a public Iranian holiday which honoured the death of , \"the Mother of the \", the daughter of the ."}
